Text: Re Data Cc for the response Would it be fair to say that all the capacity to California and Arizona is fully subscribed Thanks jrm wrote John With regard to your first question yes there are additional design capacities to be considered The Topock lateral which consists of the three Topock points listed has a capacity of MDthd Additionally the mainline capacity going west which serves ALL of our markets in Arizona as well as California is at MDthd As for your second question the data fields that were highlighted in red were more for my reference since these required some manual reviewcorrection on my part If you need further information or explanation please feel free to contact me Thanks Elizabeth John Morris on PM To Elizabeth Brown cc Subject Data Privileged Confidential Prepared for Counsel Elizabeth thank you for responding so quickly I have two questions You have total capacity of MDthd into California Can TW simultaneously supply all these amounts or is there some lower limit for total deliveries to all meters Some of the Type cells are colored red Does the red have any meaning Thank you JRM John R Morris Vice President Economists Incorporated New Hampshire
